<plot>Clouds is the story of a physicist, Robert St. John (played by Michael Patrick Gaffney), and his quest to define the ultimate theory regarding the nature of reality. On a beach-side sabbatical, St. John meets a cynical artist, a has-been actor, a religious landlady and a beautiful and mysterious woman all who help him discover that his "theory" cannot be separated from his life and love.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?109105</url></doc>
